{"tid":1687491,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"高雄議員佔領主席台 國民黨：或動用警察抬走議員 韓國瑜：議員應和平理性","createTime":"2019-11-02T01:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T01:33:46.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0272828f5aeca7b8bf0f25a15c6eb66df7095a5","tid":1687491,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2963204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2963204&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8ClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=71219183\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2963204&h=34fa7e98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2963204</a><br />\n<br />\n記者黃佳琳／高雄報導〕高市議會今進行總預算案質詢，但因市長韓國瑜請假選總統，民進黨議員罷佔主席台，與國民黨議員爆發激烈肢體衝突，副議長陸淑美以「議員受傷流血」為由，揚言動用警察權趕走民進黨團。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜請假選總統，他就任市長後首本預算書付委，此次預算人事經費最高，預算規模更達到1465億破了高雄歷史的預算紀錄，但韓國瑜以「依法請假」為由，沒有到議會報告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%84%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E7%88%86%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E7%B1%B2%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E7%9B%A3%E7%9D%A3-%E5%9C%96-091814812.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%259B%2584%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%25B5%2581%25E8%25A1%2580%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2580%25A7%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%259D%25A3-%25E5%259C%2596-091814812.html&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8ClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=540d76df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%84%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E7%88%86%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E7%B1%B2%E7%90%86%E6%80%A7%E7%9B%A3%E7%9D%A3-%E5%9C%96-091814812.html</a><br />\n<br />\n高雄市議會10月31日審查預算時，朝野爆發流血衝突，國民黨總統參選人、高雄市長韓國瑜1日在桃園呼籲，不分藍綠、不分黨派都應理性問政、理性監督。"},{"pid":"7db91b7fcb490bdffce435b5c5f3c644c1912f1a","tid":1687491,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tiJZbCV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtiJZbCV.png&h=b3879bd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf74df459bf1e85686339ec8c2c3026ac38dcb53","tid":1687491,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T01:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYzJAWY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYzJAWY.gif&h=a0d111a7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}